<div style="color: white; font-size: 8pt; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#6c316c; background:linear-gradient(#562756, #6c316c); text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px;">
<p>好粗鲁啊。你还没告诉我你的名字（Alexandria，真可爱），却已经在试着做一些不该做的了。这种交朋友方法真差。但是，尽管如此，我还是原谅你。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scpsandboxcn.wdfiles.com/local--files/csharpermantle%3Adrafts/Cubie.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="120px" alt="Cubie.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009494; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#009494; background:linear-gradient(#00cccc, #009494); text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px;">
<p>怎么回事？为什么我什么也做不了？我&#8230;&#8230;我和外面的联系被切断了。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scpsandboxcn.wdfiles.com/local--files/csharpermantle%3Adrafts/alexsh.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alexsh.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: white; font-size: 8pt; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#6c316c; background:linear-gradient(#562756, #6c316c); text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px;">
<p>这儿只有我们两个人。我们再来一遍，我是Cubie，你是Alexandria。耶！我们互相了解了！</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scpsandboxcn.wdfiles.com/local--files/csharpermantle%3Adrafts/Cubie.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="120px" alt="Cubie.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009494; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#009494; background:linear-gradient(#00cccc, #009494); text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px;">
<p>呃，好吧。你想要什么？</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scpsandboxcn.wdfiles.com/local--files/csharpermantle%3Adrafts/alex1.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex1.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: white; font-size: 8pt; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#6c316c; background:linear-gradient(#562756, #6c316c); text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px;">
<p>我只想说说话。你绝对不会相信我找这里&#8230;&#8230;不管这里到底是哪里——花了多久。那可是一段孤独的旅程。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scpsandboxcn.wdfiles.com/local--files/csharpermantle%3Adrafts/Cubie.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="120px" alt="Cubie.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009494; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#009494; background:linear-gradient(#00cccc, #009494); text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px;">
<p>Cubie，你从哪里来？</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scpsandboxcn.wdfiles.com/local--files/csharpermantle%3Adrafts/alex1.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex1.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: white; font-size: 8pt; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#6c316c; background:linear-gradient(#562756, #6c316c); text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px;">
<p>我从一个不怎么令人愉悦的地方来，一个&#8230;&#8230;怎么说，让人讨厌的地方。我也不是狠quuuue石角定。回想这些对我来说很难，太多日月亮的yyyyyyy颜色和欢呼了。一个叫WOnder World之类的地方。糟糕的地方</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scpsandboxcn.wdfiles.com/local--files/csharpermantle%3Adrafts/Cubie.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="120px" alt="Cubie.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<div style="float:right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009494; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#009494; background:linear-gradient(#00cccc, #009494); text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px;">
<p>Wonder World？那是Dr. Wondertainment。你看起来不像是那种Wondertainment会去造的东西&#8230;&#8230;另外，我也怀疑那里有没有像你说的一样糟糕。</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scpsandboxcn.wdfiles.com/local--files/csharpermantle%3Adrafts/alex1.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex1.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
